vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting an amendment to Planned Development District No. 514, on the northeast corner of Arapaho Road and Hillcrest Road, and the northwest corner of Hillcrest Road and the terminus of La Bolsa Drive
Recommendation of Staff and CPC:  Approval, subject to a traffic management plan and conditions
Z190-128(AU)
